  "description_snippet": "**VULNERABILITY DETAILS**   \nThis report describes same behavior affecting two different dialogs, but filing together since they're closely related.  \n  \nIn Android, the Bluetooth and USB chooser dialogs use a cross-origin frame's origin [1] instead of the top-level page's origin. Per https://crbug."
